modShortDescription: This 7DTD mod adds two double doors, one two meters tall, the other three meters tall.
modDescription:
This 7DTD mod adds two double [doors](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-doors/), one two meters tall, the other three meters tall.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/DelStryker/Delmod/tree/master/Delmod_Double_Door)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11141-del-stryker-a17-modlet-collection/).
